{"tid":2233742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：貴租恐添港人不滿","createTime":"2020-10-07T10:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T11:29:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2300e593bf756fec8e3b6be8936b90bb0af1cbd7","tid":2233742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/HTDNLIWR5NAY5KJRJENRQWFMO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FHTDNLIWR5NAY5KJRJENRQWFMO4%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmbnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=e16ef5f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FHTDNLIWR5NAY5KJRJENRQWFMO4%2F&h=ba19b17b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/HTDNLIWR5NAY5KJRJENRQWFMO4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n彭博：貴租恐添港人不滿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sXKXNk165wvXKBvRfkdIGX2XxFI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SV7KXGLEABFT7MTPAMGPAGSGLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsXKXNk165wvXKBvRfkdIGX2XxFI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSV7KXGLEABFT7MTPAMGPAGSGLU.jpg&h=fb3f3a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■即使肺炎疫情打擊經濟，但本港劏房租金仍高踞不下。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】肺炎疫情打擊市道，但劏房租金仍高踞不下，有外媒預料香港將面臨新的不滿情緒。彭博近日訪問了一名55歲、早前在一間蔬菜運送公司工作的Herman Wong，過往他在深圳一直以4,200元人民幣月租單位居住，過境香港工作。但隨着4月份其公司倒閉後，他有一段長時間曾流浪香港街頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劏房住戶感「被遺棄」<br />\n<br />\nHerman表示，現時透過非營利組織申請政府補貼，與人合租面積約為60方呎，即約半個停車位的旅館，月租5,000港幣。由於四周環境惡劣，並且瀰漫老鼠臭味，故必須常年關窗。<br />\n<br />\nHerman還要擔心，若客房租金回升，恐怕很快連現時住處也租不起。他認為，港府扶貧力度未夠，令其有「被遺棄」的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n由非政府組織接觸的露宿者數量，在2019年4月到2020年3月期間，由1,297增加到1,423人。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"678a2a767c3ca5b7ab5222a26eb3b8ecc59c4d56","tid":2233742,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"有錢移民去外國<br />\n無錢移民大灣區<br />\n問題自然解決"},{"pid":"98771a2a0175c0a69473b67cd0e0aac46f0c19ba","tid":2233742,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"班廢老係19841997支那二十年150人個時做過D咩"},{"pid":"9de64ace669650b65c28ad2c11a54a4965269a7b","tid":2233742,"uid":256059,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"又想將所有問題都係房屋問題"}]}